no right to live.

90
00:10:01,410 --> 00:10:03,201
Remember, you're a human with a soul...

91
00:10:03,287 --> 00:10:05,956
...and the divine gift of articulate speech.

92
00:10:06,123 --> 00:10:09,123
Your native language is the language
of Shakespeare and...

93
00:10:09,209 --> 00:10:13,373
